				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If a game doesn't have CHR-ROM, it uses CHR-RAM. The emulator doesn't have to load anything, the game code will take care of filling the CHR-RAM with the data the game will use, you just have to make that memory writable.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

